<p class="DE1"><b>The Silver Command Imperium</b> <i>(commonly referred as TSCI)</i> is a game and group where you can hangout, roleplay, go to war, patrol, join events and be a part of an good community.</p>

<p class="DE">About</p>

<p class="A1"><b>TSCI</b> is a game focused on roleplaying, they are tasked to protect the border from the rebels that are trying to take control of it and to maintain peace.</p>

